03:21.760 --> 03:23.830 align:middle line:84%
You'd be really
intentional about actually

03:23.830 --> 03:25.390 align:middle line:90%
what you're asking for.

03:25.390 --> 03:28.120 align:middle line:84%
You definitely would
not ask for a CV,

03:28.120 --> 03:32.080 align:middle line:84%
