hard conversations, how

07:28.230 --> 07:30.570 align:middle line:84%
to sort people through
performance review work

07:30.570 --> 07:32.190 align:middle line:84%
and performance
improvement plans

07:32.190 --> 07:34.380 align:middle line:84%
and ultimately potentially
letting someone go.

07:34.380 --> 07:37.980 align:middle line:84%
And so do that out of
respect for everyone

07:37.980 --> 07:39.982 align:middle line:84%
involved as soon as
you can because it's

07:39.982 --> 07:41.190 align:middle line:90%
going to be the right choice.

07:41.190 --> 07:42.523 align:middle line:90%
You're never going to regret it.

07:42.523 --> 07:45.090 align:middle line:84%
In six months, in a year,
when you reflect back on it,

07:45.090 --> 07:46.590 align:middle line:84%
the only thing
